# Architecture

Five modules: **core** (scoring.py, schema.py, docs/), **scan** (scanner.py),
**serve** (hub.py, build_profile.py), **face** (static/**), **bridge** (cruise-ai-mcp/**).

Dependency direction: `scan -> core -> serve -> face`, with `bridge` alongside `core`.

Shared utilities (paths.py, profile_data.py, __init__.py, __main__.py) are
owned by maintainers, not any single module.
